        <li><strong>Inspecting thermostats and temperature sensors</strong> to verify accuracy.</li>
        <li><strong>Checking exhaust vents and airflow systems</strong> to prevent overheating.</li>
        <li><strong>Assessing grease and carbon buildup</strong> to ensure fire safety compliance.</li>
        <li><strong>Evaluating control panels and electronic circuits</strong> to detect operational failures.</li>
